
------- Panel Settings -------

#panel:overview
    background-color and border-color: change the color of the panel when in overview
    view. Overview view is when all applications are viable as well as the side panel.

.panel-button:focus
    color: the color the icons or text change to when they are clicked on or selected.
    background-color: the background color of the selected area within the panel.
    border-color: the border color of the selected area within the panel.

.panel-button:hover:overview
    border-color: the border color of an item in the panel when it is hovered over.
    background-color: the background color of an item in the panel when it is hovered over.

------- Popup Settings -------

.candidate-popup-boxpointer
    -arrow-background-color: the background color of the popup menu.
    -arrow-border-color: color of the border that surrounds the popup menu
    background-color: background color behind the popup menu.
    color: the color of the text within the popup menu
    border-color: color of borders within the popup menu

.popup-menu-item:active
    color: color of text and icons within the popup menu when hovered over
    background-color: background color of items that are hovered over within the popup menu
    border-color: border color of items within the popup menu when they are hovered over

.popup-sub-menu
    background-color: the background color of the sub-menu within the popup menu

.popup-submenu-menu-item:open
    background-color: the background color of the selected sub-menu item when not hovered over.

------- Button Settings -------